title: 12/31/21 DPS Hour 1 Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh talk CFP
itunes:title: 12/31/21 DPS Hour 1 Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh talk CFP
description:
Rob Parker and TJ Houshmandzadeh, in for Dan Patrick, kick off New Year’s Eve by talking about their NYE experiences before talking about this afternoon’s College Football Playoffs and the magnitude of Cincinnati’s match-up with Alabama! PFF Senior College Analyst Anthony Treash joins the show for all the insight before the games kick off, and Rob says that Big Ben’s last game at Heinz Field should have been LAST YEAR!
